00:11:06,390 --> 00:11:06,750
Come here.

291
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:08,320
Let me take your schoolbag.

292
00:11:08,630 --> 00:11:09,080
Manli.

293
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:09,440
Yes.

294
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:10,240
Here.

295
00:11:11,270 --> 00:11:12,510
Let me introduce you two.

296
00:11:12,670 --> 00:11:13,030
Hello.

297
00:11:13,030 --> 00:11:13,440
Hi.

298
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:14,390
I don't know you two know each other.

299
00:11:14,390 --> 00:11:15,600
This is Chen Zihao's mom, my neighbor.

300
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:16,480
Zihao's mom?

301
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:17,000
Hello.

302
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:19,000
Dingding told me so much about Zihao.

303
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:19,840
Zihao is so outstanding.

304
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:21,550
Won awards in programming, right?

305
00:11:21,550 --> 00:11:22,320
Yes.

306
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:23,080
That's wonderful.

307
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:24,510
Learn from Zihao.

308
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:25,720
Heard that?

309
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:27,320
Your mom said learn from me.

310
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:28,150
Call me "Master".

311
00:11:28,150 --> 00:11:28,790
Hey!

312
00:11:28,790 --> 00:11:30,030
Hao, don't be rude.

313
00:11:30,030 --> 00:11:30,390
It's fine

314
00:11:30,390 --> 00:11:31,200
Heard that, Hao?

315
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:31,870
Don't be rude.

316
00:11:32,030 --> 00:11:33,720
Oh right, I remember that tent.

317
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:34,960
Want to group buy with us?

318
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:35,870
What tent?

319
00:11:36,390 --> 00:11:38,200
Our class is camping at Sheshan.

320
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:38,870
You forgot?

321
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:40,120
Oh right!

322
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:42,960
Let me tell you.

323
00:11:43,390 --> 00:11:44,840
Daer's dad is a professor.

324
00:11:45,060 --> 00:11:45,480
Hey,

325
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:46,720
