350
00:12:16,480 --> 00:12:17,320
The offer ends tonight.

351
00:12:17,670 --> 00:12:18,720
That's okay. We have one at home.

352
00:12:18,870 --> 00:12:19,240
You do?

353
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:19,790
Yes, we do.

354
00:12:20,120 --> 00:12:20,510
Alright.

355
00:12:20,510 --> 00:12:21,600
Okay.

356
00:12:21,630 --> 00:12:22,480
Let's grab dinner sometime.

357
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:23,030
Sure.

358
00:12:23,270 --> 00:12:23,910
Of course.

359
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:24,630
We're off.

360
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:25,080
Bye.

361
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:26,510
