Dingding.

367
00:12:37,030 --> 00:12:37,670
What are you doing?

368
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:38,960
Wash your hands. Let's eat.

369
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:41,200
I'm looking for the tent.

370
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:42,960
Didn't you say we had one?

371
00:12:43,510 --> 00:12:43,910
We do.

372
00:12:44,750 --> 00:12:45,440
Eat your dinner.

373
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:47,440
Is it big enough

374
00:12:47,910 --> 00:12:48,750
for the three of us?

375
00:12:51,510 --> 00:12:52,480
Your dad's in retreat.

376
00:12:53,030 --> 00:12:53,910
He doesn't have time to go.

377
00:12:55,790 --> 00:12:57,240
Retreat isn't prison.

378
00:12:57,790 --> 00:12:59,000
Taking one day off should be fine.

379
00:12:59,670 --> 00:13:01,440
Is your trip more important
than Dad's work?

380
00:13:01,910 --> 00:13:03,480
I'll go camping with you.

381
00:13:04,790 --> 00:13:06,270
But they require it to be a family trip.

382
00:13:06,910 --> 00:13:07,630
You going alone

