410
00:14:35,670 --> 00:14:36,480
This is ridiculous.

411
00:14:41,030 --> 00:14:41,550
Zhiyuan.

412
00:14:42,670 --> 00:14:44,630
I understand your conflicted feelings.

413
00:14:46,150 --> 00:14:47,120
You don't want to see her.

414
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:48,630
But...

415
00:14:48,960 --> 00:14:49,910
You care about the child.

416
00:14:50,790 --> 00:14:51,440
However...

417
00:14:51,870 --> 00:14:53,600
Making you keep acting like this,

418
00:14:54,320 --> 00:14:55,630
