419
00:14:58,390 --> 00:15:00,750
You've been separated for some time now.

420
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:03,150
I know you promised to give her time

421
00:15:03,480 --> 00:15:05,440
to explain to the elders and child.

422
00:15:07,150 --> 00:15:08,480
But she keeps delaying.

423
00:15:09,440 --> 00:15:10,480
And now she's making you

424
00:15:10,630 --> 00:15:12,720
