425
00:15:14,910 --> 00:15:16,000
What does that tell you?

426
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:18,270
What does that mean?

427
00:15:20,120 --> 00:15:20,670
It means

428
00:15:20,670 --> 00:15:22,080
she doesn't want the world to know

429
00:15:22,080 --> 00:15:23,440
