430
00:15:26,080 --> 00:15:28,000
After all, it's not good news.

431
00:15:29,750 --> 00:15:31,030
Not just not good news.

432
00:15:31,600 --> 00:15:33,870
For her, it's disastrous.

433
00:15:34,390 --> 00:15:35,510
It's not because of her feelings.

434
00:15:36,120 --> 00:15:37,320
It's her public image.

435
00:15:40,750 --> 00:15:42,270
To succeed in sales,

436
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:44,000
she must present to the world

437
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:45,910
an image of perfect family life.

438
00:15:46,790 --> 00:15:47,600
What's more.

439
00:15:48,080 --> 00:15:50,000
You're not just
a university professor now

440
00:15:50,600 --> 00:15:52,080
but a popular knowledge blogger

441
00:15:53,030 --> 00:15:55,000
for high-net-worth individuals.

442
00:15:55,910 --> 00:15:57,670
Your personal brand serves as

443
00:15:58,240 --> 00:15:59,670
the best credibility endorsement for her.

444
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:01,550
This adds luster

445
00:16:01,790 --> 00:16:03,030
to her carefully crafted image.

446
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:04,910
Hu Manli knows that

447
00:16:05,550 --> 00:16:07,000
perfectly well.

448
00:16:08,120 --> 00:16:08,960
So you think

449
00:16:08,960 --> 00:16:10,270
she'd be willing to let the public know

450
00:16:10,270 --> 00:16:11,600
that you've already separated?

451
00:16:13,150 --> 00:16:14,120
Now that you mention it,

452
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:16,120
everything suddenly makes sense.

453
00:16:17,200 --> 00:16:17,790
Scheming woman.

454
00:16:19,390 --> 00:16:21,790
Still calculating at this point.

455
00:16:22,600 --> 00:16:23,360
How pathetic.

456
00:16:25,270 --> 00:16:26,270
Don't get worked up yet.

457
00:16:27,630 --> 00:16:28,750
Maybe it's just me

458
00:16:29,270 --> 00:16:32,030
measuring others' corn by my own bushel.

459
00:16:32,200 --> 00:16:32,480
No.

460
00:16:33,030 --> 00:16:34,000
Your analysis is correct,

461
00:16:34,320 --> 00:16:35,030
absolutely accurate.

462
00:16:35,240 --> 00:16:36,120
That's how she is.

463
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:38,550
It seems

464
00:16:39,200 --> 00:16:40,390
those last bits of pity for her

465
00:16:40,840 --> 00:16:41,840
aren't necessary anymore.

466
00:16:52,780 --> 00:16:54,780
[Have meeting that day.
Tell son our separation ASAP]

467
00:17:08,500 --> 00:17:08,920
[Hu Manli]

468
00:17:46,790 --> 00:17:47,640
At the beginning,

469
00:17:47,720 --> 00:17:49,510
all that neighborhood gossip,

