00:17:49,510 --> 00:17:50,790
I didn't take it seriously.

471
00:17:51,510 --> 00:17:53,270
I thought since my dad just passed away,

472
00:17:54,590 --> 00:17:56,680
and that man
is 20 years younger than Mom,

473
00:17:56,960 --> 00:17:57,880
