474
00:17:58,200 --> 00:17:58,480
Right?

475
00:17:58,640 --> 00:17:59,240
Exactly.

476
00:17:59,790 --> 00:18:00,680
But later,

477
00:18:00,960 --> 00:18:01,920
the neighbors told me

478
00:18:02,510 --> 00:18:03,480
that man

479
00:18:03,750 --> 00:18:05,750
