480
00:18:05,750 --> 00:18:06,550
all the time.

481
00:18:07,070 --> 00:18:07,510
Then,

482
00:18:08,200 --> 00:18:09,070
I realized it's not right.

483
00:18:09,440 --> 00:18:10,960
He's getting so close with my mom

484
00:18:11,240 --> 00:18:12,680
while hiding another woman at home.

485
00:18:12,790 --> 00:18:13,440
What does that say?

486
00:18:14,790 --> 00:18:15,920
This is disastrous!

487
00:18:16,550 --> 00:18:17,310
Let me tell you.

488
00:18:17,750 --> 00:18:19,350
Your mom met a con artist!

489
00:18:20,310 --> 00:18:22,110
My mom already came clean with me.

490
00:18:22,160 --> 00:18:23,680
Said they're going on a trip.

491
00:18:23,960 --> 00:18:25,350
Even planned a European tour.

492
00:18:28,070 --> 00:18:29,240
The scammer's closing in.

493
00:18:29,310 --> 00:18:30,750
The mask's about to drop, you see?

494
00:18:31,070 --> 00:18:31,510
Right?

495
00:18:31,830 --> 00:18:32,960
That's exactly what I think!

496
00:18:33,750 --> 00:18:35,160
Manli, I'm telling you I'm really

497
00:18:35,720 --> 00:18:36,790
freaking out here.

498
00:18:37,030 --> 00:18:38,440
My mom's like an old house on fire.

499
00:18:38,750 --> 00:18:40,110
No ambulance or firetruck

500
00:18:40,110 --> 00:18:41,030
