514
00:19:18,270 --> 00:19:19,000
That much?

515
00:19:19,000 --> 00:19:19,580
Yes.

516
00:19:22,960 --> 00:19:23,640
Let me tell you.

517
00:19:24,510 --> 00:19:25,310
This con artist

518
00:19:25,640 --> 00:19:27,160
