519
00:19:27,640 --> 00:19:29,400
I was thinking the exact same!

520
00:19:29,880 --> 00:19:31,830
Who will pay for their trips?

521
00:19:32,000 --> 00:19:32,920
Definitely my mom!

522
00:19:33,240 --> 00:19:34,640
Right! Once they're abroad,

523
00:19:34,920 --> 00:19:36,270
this guy sweet-talks her.

524
00:19:36,440 --> 00:19:37,270
Mom gets confused

525
00:19:37,270 --> 00:19:39,000
