526
00:19:39,350 --> 00:19:39,960
Listen to me.

527
00:19:40,440 --> 00:19:41,480
Money's one thing.

528
00:19:41,640 --> 00:19:42,960
But she could get hurt.

529
00:19:42,960 --> 00:19:43,420
What?

530
00:19:44,200 --> 00:19:45,510
Saw that recent movie?

531
00:19:45,590 --> 00:19:46,790
