546
00:20:24,790 --> 00:20:25,400
Sorry about that.

547
00:20:25,790 --> 00:20:26,790
Just started in insurance.

548
00:20:26,790 --> 00:20:28,240
Not the sharpest tool.

549
00:20:29,030 --> 00:20:30,640
Pretty dumb, really.

550
00:20:31,640 --> 00:20:32,160
Miss Sun...

551
00:20:35,350 --> 00:20:36,350
Sun Jie, don't worry.

552
00:20:36,480 --> 00:20:37,880
I'll handle this matter.

553
00:20:40,200 --> 00:20:41,720
Thank you, Manli. I trust you.

554
00:20:42,750 --> 00:20:44,510
I hate liars the most!

555
00:20:44,680 --> 00:20:45,160
Exactly!

556
00:20:54,110 --> 00:20:55,350
Hu Manli, what are you doing?

557
00:20:56,440 --> 00:20:57,550
You said there was a deal.

558
00:20:57,550 --> 00:20:58,640
I heard gossip all morning.

559
00:20:59,720 --> 00:21:01,200
And you call me unreliable?

560
00:21:01,200 --> 00:21:02,880
You almost ruined this deal!

561
00:21:04,160 --> 00:21:04,750
What do you mean?

562
00:21:07,160 --> 00:21:07,920
