569
00:21:23,030 --> 00:21:23,790
Why come to you?

570
00:21:24,310 --> 00:21:25,640
That's called client retention.

571
00:21:26,030 --> 00:21:27,270
Even she can't convince her mom,

572
00:21:27,270 --> 00:21:28,400
